{"tid":1939470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯成功爭取：建議政府研禁止非香港居民從各口岸入境","createTime":"2020-03-23T07:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T07:15:11.000Z","uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4eab8b559b3d2c11a5901bf4a7bfc689d1f2adb4","tid":1939470,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"民建聯建議政府研禁止非香港居民從各口岸入境<br />\n12分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】民建聯形容，未來兩、三周是防疫關鍵期，政府有必要採取非常措施，建議政府強制入境人士進行病毒測試，有需要時應該徵用酒店並暫停酒吧及戲院運作。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯建議政府研究禁止非香港居民從各個口岸入境香港，不過他們憂慮全面封關會影響貨流。<br />\n<br />\n對於家居檢疫，他們認為政府有必要與檢疫手帶的供應商研究如何修補漏洞，當局又應該加強執法並設立專門舉報熱線。"},{"pid":"f2733057292c0831ae1c248baec3f41ce1d4548a","tid":1939470,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385379&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfry2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a0e0fe42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385379&h=b1413d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=385379</a>"},{"pid":"3c4bed53aa44a7e06fa751ab5ffbd2897cb1bacf","tid":1939470,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951b9c726ac0931f905684758ed90731cdb9c2e9","tid":1939470,"uid":168564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"應該會除咗中國人之外"},{"pid":"438387ad74c2698aee36f4ea583479e888296e5a","tid":1939470,"uid":39855,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T07:14:36.000Z","msg":"多數已經由政府夾好左，再由民建聯放風拎分，屌佢老味！"},{"pid":"ad043c086d9f7d6e6a154930a1bf995a65652236","tid":1939470,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"